title: Download "KeenGo" Now !
content:
KeenGo

FEATURES:
*Enhanced AdLib Music for Keen Dreams (works with all keens once Keen Dreams has been activated)
*AntiAliasing
*Play any Keen you want through DosBox with the touch of a button

When everything is set up, press 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 or D to play that particular episode.

If your having any problems, read the "TroubleShooting Tips.txt"

If you would like the DosBox configurations changed, you can edit the config for each game in "C:\CommanderKeen\KeenGoDataFiles". Just open the "K#Config.k" in notepad and save it.

Xtra, if you get the chance can you upload this on spatang, because my link to the download expires in 7 days. Thanks.
